<br>
Extremly fun flash game. You have a castle and need to stop charging troops. <br>
<br>
Some helpful advice:<br>
<br>
1. Stop the stickfigure attackers. You do that through picking them up and throw them high up in the air. When they land the splat!<br>
<br>
2. Try saving up money to buy a temple as fast as possible. When you have a temple you can drag a stickfigure into your castle. Doing that and you recruit that attacker. When the pillar of light dissapears you can recruit another one.<br>
<br>
3. Build either archer range or mana pool next. The recruited attackers can be trained to become archers or wizards. But beware of building too many cause there will be upkeep cost. After awhile you can have your own army!<br>
<br>
4. Giants can't be picked up and must be killed by spells. Use A, D and S as hotkeys for your spells. 1, 2 and 3 works aswell.<br>
<br>
